platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: From the developer that brought the superb board game Carcassonne to iOS comes a fiendishly tricky puzzler thatll test your memory and your reflexes. To clear each set of colorful tiles, youll need to follow specific rules in orderlike removing odd-numbered tiles first, then ones with animalsbefore the clock runs out. Each super-short level is more tense and demanding than the last, making it that much more satisfying when you clean the board and progress to the next challenge.
